      "codeText": "# ROT13 (shift 13)\necho \"Uryyb\" | tr 'A-Za-z' 'N-ZA-Mn-za-m'\n\n# Try all 25 shifts\npython3 -c \"\ns = 'Khoor'\nfor i in range(26):\n    print(i, ''.join(chr((ord(c)-65+i)%26+65) if c.isupper()\n                     else chr((ord(c)-97+i)%26+97) if c.islower()\n                     else c for c in s))\n\"",
